                        "The Healing Power: The subconscious mind controls all vital functions of your body. By flooding it with thoughts of health, vitality, and peace, you can accelerate physical and mental healing.",
                        "Forgiveness is Freedom: Resentment and holding grudges act as poison in your subconscious mind. To experience true peace and manifest your desires, you must completely forgive yourself and others."
